00:38:32.000 --> 00:38:33.000
Matalino.

00:38:33.250 --> 00:38:34.850
Bumangon ka na. Wag kang uupo sa upuan ko.

00:38:34.880 --> 00:38:36.540
Umupo ka sa sofa diyan.

00:38:37.860 --> 00:38:40.060
Ang opisina ng ministro ay kahanga-hanga.

00:38:41.030 --> 00:38:41.960
Umupo ka.

00:38:45.960 --> 00:38:47.820
Bakit hindi mo sinabi sa akin bago ka dumating?

00:38:47.820 --> 00:38:49.560
Bakit sumulpot nang wala sa oras na ganito?

00:38:49.560 --> 00:38:51.360
Sa iyo, kailangan kong kumilos bigla.

00:38:51.550 --> 00:38:53.680
Kung hindi, magkakaroon ka ng oras upang maghanda.

00:38:56.960 --> 00:38:57.570
Ano ang problema?

00:38:57.570 --> 00:38:59.030
Anong kakila-kilabot na tsaa ito?

00:38:59.190 --> 00:39:00.110
Grabe ang lasa.

00:39:00.110 --> 00:39:02.340
Sa susunod dalhan kita ng masarap na tsaa.

00:39:02.480 --> 00:39:03.550
Magpasalamat na mayroon kang anumang tsaa.

00:39:03.550 --> 00:39:04.630
Huwag masyadong mapili.

00:39:06.700 --> 00:39:08.100
Ang sarap lang sa akin.

00:39:11.190 --> 00:39:12.440
Nandito ka sa isang business trip?

00:39:12.440 --> 00:39:13.440
Oo, sa negosyo.

00:39:13.580 --> 00:39:15.790
At mayroon akong mahalagang bagay

00:39:15.960 --> 00:39:17.480
mag-ulat kay Ministro Wen.

00:39:18.490 --> 00:39:19.820
Anong mahalagang bagay?

00:39:23.150 --> 00:39:25.350
I-treat mo muna ako sa hapunan.

00:39:25.590 --> 00:39:27.320
Maaari nating pag-usapan ito habang kumakain.

00:39:27.480 --> 00:39:28.960
Huwag mo akong hulaan.

00:39:30.710 --> 00:39:31.760
Kailangan din kitang bilhan ng hapunan?

00:39:31.760 --> 00:39:32.470
Syempre.

00:39:34.000 --> 00:39:34.920
hindi ba ako sayo

00:39:36.540 --> 00:39:37.350
panauhin?

00:39:39.440 --> 00:39:40.150
Bilisan mo.

00:39:40.150 --> 00:39:42.070
Bilisan mo ano? Naka-duty pa ako.

00:39:42.230 --> 00:39:44.100
Hintayin mo ako sa restaurant sa ibaba.

00:39:44.100 --> 00:39:45.250
Pagkatapos kong tapusin ang aking trabaho,

00:39:45.250 --> 00:39:46.590
Pupunta ako kaagad kapag nakaalis na ako.

00:39:46.590 --> 00:39:47.650
Ililibre kita ng hapunan.

00:39:47.650 --> 00:39:48.360
Ang treat ko.

00:39:48.800 --> 00:39:49.440
ayos lang.

00:39:51.510 --> 00:39:52.440
Magandang balita!

00:39:53.320 --> 00:39:53.920
Mabuti.

00:40:01.920 --> 00:40:02.680
pinuno,

00:40:03.190 --> 00:40:05.390
anong klaseng tao ang ating Ministro Wen?

00:40:05.550 --> 00:40:07.530
Kailangan kong malaman nang maaga ang tungkol sa kanya.

00:40:07.530 --> 00:40:08.530
Huwag kang mag-alala.

00:40:08.920 --> 00:40:11.400
Si Ministro Wen ay kaakit-akit at matikas,

00:40:11.420 --> 00:40:12.670
gwapo at talented.

00:40:12.670 --> 00:40:13.510
Siya ay may kultura kapag kailangan

00:40:13.510 --> 00:40:14.880
at malakas kapag kinakailangan.

00:40:14.880 --> 00:40:16.740
Siguradong mabubusog ka.

00:40:16.810 --> 00:40:17.600
Mabuti.

00:40:18.480 --> 00:40:19.680
Nandito si Minister Wen.

00:40:20.210 --> 00:40:20.640
Zhao.

00:40:21.440 --> 00:40:22.030
Wen.

00:40:23.000 --> 00:40:23.930
May bisita ka.

00:40:24.830 --> 00:40:26.190
Pakilala ko.

00:40:26.670 --> 00:40:27.870
Miss Huang Lingling.

00:40:29.630 --> 00:40:30.590
Hindi natin siya matatawag na Miss,

00:40:30.590 --> 00:40:31.920
Kasamang Huang Lingling.

00:40:31.920 --> 00:40:33.120
Ito ay si Minister Wen.

00:40:33.510 --> 00:40:34.710
Hello, Chief. Natutuwa akong makilala ka.

00:40:34.710 --> 00:40:36.170
Hello. Mangyaring umupo.

00:40:36.920 --> 00:40:37.480
Umupo ka.

00:40:37.480 --> 00:40:38.190
Mabuti.

00:40:43.360 --> 00:40:44.190
Mabuti.

00:40:47.360 --> 00:40:48.150
tingnan mo,

00:40:48.630 --> 00:40:50.560
na-order na namin lahat ng paborito mo.

00:40:54.000 --> 00:40:55.630
Kayong dalawa ay napakahalagang pinuno.

00:40:55.630 --> 00:40:57.880
Bakit pumili ng isang maliit na restawran?

00:40:58.250 --> 00:40:59.720
Kung ang kalinisan ay hindi naaayon sa pamantayan,

00:40:59.720 --> 00:41:01.120
at magkasakit ka,

00:41:01.190 --> 00:41:02.520
kakila-kilabot iyan!

00:41:02.680 --> 00:41:03.540
Kasamang Huang,

00:41:03.980 --> 00:41:06.060
saan ka kadalasan kumakain?

00:41:07.630 --> 00:41:08.920
Sa Nanjing West Road, mayroon

00:41:08.920 --> 00:41:10.920
ilang magagandang Western restaurant.

00:41:11.440 --> 00:41:13.640
Sa susunod i-treat kita ng kainan doon.

00:41:18.810 --> 00:41:20.120
Actually, kami na

00:41:20.230 --> 00:41:21.280
sanay matipid,

00:41:21.280 --> 00:41:22.940
lalo na ang ating Ministro Wen.

00:41:23.440 --> 00:41:24.440
Kita mo, malapit na tayong mamatay

00:41:24.440 --> 00:41:26.030
napakaraming beses.

00:41:26.070 --> 00:41:27.320
Hindi talaga kami sanay

00:41:27.320 --> 00:41:28.670
yung mga foreign dishes.

00:41:29.600 --> 00:41:30.550
Walang problema yun.

00:41:30.550 --> 00:41:32.950
May mga Chinese restaurant din doon.

00:41:33.010 --> 00:41:33.800
Mabuti.

00:41:34.000 --> 00:41:35.530
Sa susunod hahanap ako ng pagkakataon

00:41:35.760 --> 00:41:37.020
para magkaisa tayo.

00:41:38.840 --> 00:41:40.170
Tumpak ba ang iyong relo?

00:41:41.710 --> 00:41:43.170
Ang relo? Napaka tumpak.

00:41:43.400 --> 00:41:44.600
Lubhang tumpak.

00:41:45.280 --> 00:41:46.810
Miss Huang, hindi mo alam.

00:41:47.230 --> 00:41:50.840
Ang relo na ito ay regalo mula kay Minister Wen.

00:41:51.760 --> 00:41:52.880
Ito ang pinaka

00:41:52.900 --> 00:41:54.430
mahalaga at mahalagang regalo

00:41:54.630 --> 00:41:56.190
Natanggap ko na sa buhay ko.

00:41:56.190 --> 00:41:58.320
Isinusuot ko ito araw at gabi.

00:41:58.630 --> 00:41:59.690
Yan ang tawag mo,

00:41:59.800 --> 00:42:00.650
ano ang parirala...

00:42:00.650 --> 00:42:02.460
malapit bilang mga panloob na organo.

00:42:04.070 --> 00:42:05.300
Hindi ganoon kahalaga ang relo na ito.

00:42:05.300 --> 00:42:07.160
Binili ko ito sa isang secondhand stall.

00:42:07.710 --> 00:42:09.440
Kinakalawang lahat ang mga bahagi noon.

00:42:09.590 --> 00:42:10.760
Ako mismo ang nag-ayos.

00:42:11.800 --> 00:42:12.780
Sana ay tumpak ito.

00:42:12.780 --> 00:42:14.240
tumpak. Napaka tumpak.

00:42:14.800 --> 00:42:17.130
At ano ang pariralang ginamit mo kanina,

00:42:17.440 --> 00:42:18.900
malapit sa mga panloob na organo?

00:42:19.760 --> 00:42:21.790
Ang ibig mong sabihin ay 'malapit sa balat', tama ba?

00:42:21.790 --> 00:42:23.710
Tama, malapit sa balat ko.

00:42:24.040 --> 00:42:25.850
Huwag gumamit ng mga parirala sa maling paraan.

00:42:25.880 --> 00:42:26.630
Tara kain na tayo.

00:42:28.670 --> 00:42:30.670
Mga maling salita, nagsasalita ng walang kapararakan.

00:42:36.190 --> 00:42:36.880
Huang,

00:42:37.920 --> 00:42:39.850
Umorder din ako ng plain noodle soup.

00:42:39.880 --> 00:42:41.100
Maaari mo bang tingnan ito?

00:42:41.100 --> 00:42:42.110
titingnan ko.

00:42:42.110 --> 00:42:43.360
Bilisan mo sila.

00:42:48.960 --> 00:42:49.710
paano ito?

00:42:51.480 --> 00:42:52.550
Siya ay mula sa timog.

00:42:52.960 --> 00:42:55.030
Mataas ang pinag-aralan at masining.

00:42:55.670 --> 00:42:56.600
Anong ibig mong sabihin?

00:42:57.880 --> 00:42:59.010
Ipakilala mo sya sakin?

00:43:00.230 --> 00:43:01.230
Itigil ang pagpapanggap.

00:43:01.320 --> 00:43:02.230
Itigil ang pagiging mapili.

00:43:02.230 --> 00:43:03.480
Sapat na siya.

00:43:03.670 --> 00:43:04.800
Kilala mo pa ba siya?

00:43:07.280 --> 00:43:08.840
Paano pa kayo nagkakilala

00:43:10.840 --> 00:43:11.960
babaeng ganyan?

00:43:14.880 --> 00:43:15.940
Sige, sige.

00:43:15.960 --> 00:43:17.020
Tara kain na tayo dali,

00:43:17.480 --> 00:43:19.210
at aalis na kami pagtapos namin.

00:43:24.030 --> 00:43:25.630
Parang asong kumagat kay Lv Dongbin,

00:43:26.110 --> 00:43:27.280
hindi mo nakikilala ang mabuting hangarin.

